[size=6]Installation[/size]

[list=1]
[*]Mods are installed by dropping [b]unzipped[/b] .zip files in the Battle Brothers data directory (e.g. C:\GOG Games\Battle Brothers\data). Leave them unzipped! You don't have to worry about mod load order.
[*]Required mods: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/battlebrothers/mods/60]Legends mod[/url] (gameplay overhaul; you may need the latest from their GitHub. Install both the asset and gameplay mods), [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/battlebrothers/mods/685]Modern Hooks[/url], and [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/battlebrothers/mods/479]MSU[/url]
[*]Drop the .zip downloaded from here into the data directory
[/list]
I'm experimenting with Nexus API uploads which is a new feature and when you try to download from nexus it can show up as something like a UID (see below); you can just rename it to mod_lewd-X.X.X.zip or something (add .zip extension).
[img]https://cdn.imgpile.com/f/VtJH6vv_xl.png[/img]

The [url=https://github.com/PerplexedPeach/battle_brothers_lewd]GitHub repository[/url] also has the latest version and updated roadmap. You'll need to download it from the release, not from the source.
[img]https://cdn.imgpile.com/f/7K2aXpc_xl.png[/img]

[size=6]Getting Started[/size]

This mod centers on a [b]female avatar[/b] character. You need to play an [b]avatar origin[/b] (Lone Wolf, Berserker, Courtesan, or any origin that gives you a player-controlled main character).

[b]Female avatar[/b]: If your avatar is female from the start, you are ready. Progress through the heel event chain (see Transformation Event Chains below) to unlock traits, abilities, and perk trees.

[b]Male avatar[/b]: If your avatar is male, you need to fight [b]Hexen[/b] in battle. After the fight, a curse event chain will trigger that gradually transforms your character into a woman. Once the transformation is complete, the normal progression (heels, Dainty, Delicate, Ethereal) takes over.

[b]Progression summary[/b]:
[list=1]
[*]Gain company renown to trigger the first heel event. Wear heels taller than your current skill to level up.
[*]Progress through heel stages to earn the [b]Dainty[/b] trait, then [b]Delicate[/b]. Each unlocks new perk trees and sex abilities.
[*]Take damage in combat to unlock [b]Masochism[/b] tiers (requires Delicate). Stay in the south to trigger events.
[*]Cause enough partner climaxes and fight ghosts to trigger the [b]Ethereal quest chain[/b]: three boss fights guided by a fox spirit, culminating in a supernatural transformation. This is the pinnacle: supernatural allure, succubus perk tree, tail weapon, and Blink teleport.
[/list]

Your party members will react to your progression. Male brothers may be affected by your allure, leading to events that shift based on your Domination/Submission score.

[size=6]Overview[/size]

This mod brings lewdness into the world of Battle Brothers in an immersive, balanced, and gratifying way. Its contents are NSFW and only for adults 18+!

New mechanics, event images, character sprites, item sprites, custom sounds, and writing are tightly integrated to provide a quality experience. All event writing is documented [url=https://lewdhammer.miraheze.org/wiki/Battle_Brothers]on the wiki[/url] if you just want to read them.

Sexual themes include: female protagonist, high heels, transformation, bondage, domination loss, submission, seduction, domination, harassment, battlefuck

[size=6]Features[/size]

[size=5]Allure and Beauty System[/size]
[list]
[*][b]Allure[/b] is a new character stat derived from your traits, equipment, melee defense, and heels. It is the core currency for seduction and beauty mechanics.
[*][b]Entrancing Beauty[/b]: A passive aura that can inflict Horny (or on crit, Horny + Stunned) on nearby enemies each turn and after movement. Chance scales with Allure vs target Resolve and distance. Allied male brothers can also be affected, though they get a significant Resolve bonus against it.
[*][b]Pheromones[/b]: Self-cast buff that boosts Entrancing Beauty's chance and adds a pink glow effect.
[/list]

Dynamic sounds and animated quotes on skill use (Entrancing Beauty shown):
