[list]
[*][b]Seduce[/b]: Ranged active ability (up to 4 tiles) that charms male enemies to fight for you. Chance: 50 + (Allure - Resolve) - 10 per tile distance. Full hit chance breakdown shown per target on hover.
[/list]

[size=5]Pleasure and Climax System[/size]
[list]
[*]All characters with lewd traits gain a [b]Pleasure[/b] resource in combat. When Pleasure reaches PleasureMax, the character has a [b]Climax[/b], applying a temporary debuff.
[*][b]Orgasm Defeat[/b]: Characters can be defeated by accumulating enough orgasms. Most enemies fall after 1; tougher enemies survive more based on their Resolve and miniboss status. Player characters have much higher thresholds from traits and perks, and go unconscious (recoverable) rather than dying.
[*]Pleasure sources: masochism (damage taken), and five sex ability types (see below).
[*]Enemies with humanoid bodies automatically gain PleasureMax based on their Resolve.
[/list]
