[size=5]Transformation Event Chains[/size]

[b]Heel Progression (Dainty / Delicate)[/b]:
[list]
[*]Stage 0 to 1 event triggers based on company renown; further stages require heel skill thresholds.
[*]Increase heel skill by wearing heels taller than your current height. The bigger the difference, the faster you progress.
[*]Custom heel walking sounds on different terrain types!
[*]Progression: Normal to Dainty to Delicate, each granting new traits, allure bonuses, and perk tree access.
[/list]

