[b]Ethereal Quest Chain[/b]:
[list]
[*]After reaching Delicate with enough climaxes, fighting ghosts triggers an encounter with the spirit of an ancient fox spirit who offers a pact.
[*]Three sequential combat stages, each with a unique boss:
[list]
[*][b]The Faithless[/b]: A bandit camp led by a named boss who spurned the spirit in life.
[*][b]The Beast[/b]: An unhold lair with "The Ancient One", a boss with a unique piledriver ability that grabs and pleasures targets.
[*][b]The Killer[/b]: A broodthing lair in a corrupted swamp. A kraken-style tentacle boss with 8 tentacles, an AoE pleasure attack (Ravage), and a custom ensnare that applies pleasure and Horny per turn.
[/list][*]The final stage culminates in the spirit merging with you and the Ethereal transformation. Rich multi-screen narrative throughout.
[*]Culminates in the Ethereal trait: the pinnacle transformation with enhanced allure, additional perk points, unique cosmetic changes, and the Succubus perk tree.
[/list]
